kydra (0.9.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fixed settings dialog functionality for version columns
  * Added immediate feedback when toggling version column settings
  * Improved signal communication between settings dialog and main window
  * Added dedicated column visibility control methods
  * Fixed dependency installation issues with qapt and libkf5config5
  * Fixed icon theme installation in Debian package
  * Fixed settings persistence for column visibility

